data.Name: Jidenna
data.Bio: Jidenna Theodore Mobisson, known synonymously as Jidenna, (born April 5, 1985 in Wisconsin Rapids, Wisconsin)[1] is an American musical artist and performer. He is signed to Janelle Monáe's Wondaland Records label[11] and distributed through Epic Records. He has collaborated with numerous artists, including Roman GianArthur, St. Beauty, Deep Cotton and Janelle Monáe herself, recording a five-song compilation EP titled The Eephus.[12] In February 2015 Read more on Last.fm
